{"tid":794803,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[轉貼] 九龍公園游泳池奇遇記","createTime":"2018-08-26T13:51:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-10T13:36:12.000Z","uid":130303,"like":33,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"68bd5afc3ed636527f852ceacc2fbc7baa3a6987","tid":794803,"uid":130303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T13:51:41.000Z","msg":"九龍公園游泳池係時下年青人最喜歡既游泳池之一 , 入場費是： <br />\na）平日= HKD 17<br />\nb）週末/公眾假期= HKD 19 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/08/26/8Tgljo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F08%2F26%2F8Tgljo.jpg&h=7b256b8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n九龍公園游泳池 入口<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/08/26/m8eNQJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F08%2F26%2Fm8eNQJ.jpg&h=4cee9674&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n泳池大約有40-50張甲板, 好多人喜歡係度曬日光浴...<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/08/26/0mBRSt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F08%2F26%2F0mBRSt.jpg&h=8a147e9c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n無法理解訓係地板上曬黑......難道佢地唔覺得熱？<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/08/26/Q7ynez.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F08%2F26%2FQ7ynez.jpg&h=be18caae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n泳池陽光燦爛，你可能會發現, 真正游水既人其實唔多<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/08/26/DwMdvS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F08%2F26%2FDwMdvS.jpg&h=dbb6c709&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/08/26/Uc8Hqt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F08%2F26%2FUc8Hqt.jpg&h=f0ff75bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢度既日光浴區非常適合想曬黑身體既人！佢同游泳池分開 - 沒有救生員睇住你 。有人會拉低泳褲曬八月十五，呢種情景係呢度可以講係幾常見<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/i9prHF3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fi9prHF3.jpg&h=91c37ba7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有一部分更衣室既淋浴間只係用窗簾隔開 ，所以，如果你好好彩， 你可以睇到你隔離游泳運動員，為你舉辦一場表演， 因為佢地當中大多數人都非常樂意接受你既愛撫！你也可以享受佢地係你面前裸露淋浴既場景.... <br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/spJNeeh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FspJNeeh.jpg&h=caa3d83b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/08/26/mXQPg9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F08%2F26%2FmXQPg9.jpg&h=ba9c5c92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/LkhqMOK.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FLkhqMOK.jpg&d=Y%2FW%2FCsZJIoYQ15%2FbMY8nJzCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=6727e3ed\" target=\"_blank\">https://i.imgur.com/LkhqMOK.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\n係更衣室, 你會隨處見到咩都無著既男人用吹風機吹乾個頭同身體, 任何身材既男人都一覽無為。<br />\n<br />\n係九龍公園游泳池, 年青人可以享受一個美好既周末下午。"},{"pid":"01e08c68e6059db870aeec0d292024c59812e37a","tid":794803,"uid":45693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T13:52:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83764dbdfbfb7659ac8cef5d8725ce02901cf77a","tid":794803,"uid":116330,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T13:55:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/spJNeeh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FspJNeeh.jpg&h=caa3d83b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/08/26/mXQPg9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F08%2F26%2FmXQPg9.jpg&h=ba9c5c92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/LkhqMOK.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FLkhqMOK.jpg&d=Y%2FW%2FCsZJIoYQ15%2FbMY8nJzCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=6727e3ed\" target=\"_blank\">https://i.imgur.com/LkhqMOK.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\n係更衣室, 你會隨處見到咩都無著既男人用吹風機吹乾個頭同身體, 任何身材既男人都一覽無為。<br />\n<br />\n係九龍公園游泳池, 年青人可以享受一個美好既周末下午。</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申,非gay"},{"pid":"b469fa5b4cd73d145aa04e108bc58a84de863aa5","tid":794803,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T14:04:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00d11b88aed22304c3ee8e9b0c565a5b81b7e68c","tid":794803,"uid":64564,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T14:05:50.000Z","msg":"去過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37b9db89758b55349cf05d6a884f0b38b23fbae8","tid":794803,"uid":47170,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T14:06:17.000Z","msg":"以前好似有個高登仔係九龍公園游水<br />\n之後收到張字條話想同佢做朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4375977be97a13b0c7c66cd721f98ce4fa7011f9","tid":794803,"uid":25221,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T14:07:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"be8d971554cf976ef075befa6a46b50098380fd5","tid":794803,"uid":44725,"like":17,"dislike":2,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T14:10:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/08/26/XyJNIi.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F08%2F26%2FXyJNIi.gif&h=